headline: Waters Corporation to Present at the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) announced that Udit Batra Ph.D., Waters President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference on Monday, January 13th, 2025 at 2:15 PM Pacific Time (5:15 PM Eastern Time).
